Exception-Sink
==============

Exception::Sink provides compact general purpose exception handling.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Exception::Sink does not use other libraries, it requires only core perl.

